91
00:05:19,630 --> 00:05:21,240
tungkol sa lahat ng opisyal ng sibil at militar.

92
00:05:21,240 --> 00:05:22,770
Dapat mong pag-aralan itong mabuti

93
00:05:23,680 --> 00:05:26,040
