sa pagmamana ng trono.

116
00:06:10,490 --> 00:06:12,820
Mas mataas ang prestihiyo ng pamilya Murong,

117
00:06:12,830 --> 00:06:14,840
mas dapat kang mag-ingat laban sa kanila.

118
00:06:14,840 --> 00:06:16,330
Inay, nagreklamo ka

119
00:06:16,360 --> 00:06:17,320
sa akin dati.

120
00:06:17,630 --> 00:06:18,680
Sabi mo hindi na-appreciate ni Father

121
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:20,040
suporta ng pamilya Zhuang

122
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:21,680
at laging nagbabantay sa kanila.

123
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:22,920
Paano mo ako matuturuan ngayon na...

124
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:23,580
Chengyang!

125
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:25,630
Ikaw na ngayon ang Emperador.

126
00:06:25,950 --> 00:06:26,680
Hindi mo dapat

127
00:06:27,310 --> 00:06:28,750
sabihin mo pa yan.

128
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:30,750
okay,

129
00:06:32,510 --> 00:06:33,390
hindi ko gagawin.

130
00:06:38,810 --> 00:06:42,450
[Murong Residence]

131
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:43,240
Congratulations, Your Highness.

132
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:44,040
Binabati kita, Prinsipe.

133
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:45,040
Salamat po sir.

134
