Pakiusap.

135
00:06:52,159 --> 00:06:53,480
Nahanap mo na ba

136
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:54,270
Feng Suige?

137
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:58,210
Personal na pinangunahan ni Jie ang paghahanap,

138
