Ning Fei!

175
00:08:20,480 --> 00:08:21,080
Tumingin ka sa akin.

176
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:24,120
sabi ko sabay tingin sakin.

177
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:27,750
Dumating ako upang makita ka ng ilang araw,

178
00:08:27,750 --> 00:08:29,280
pero hindi mo ako kinakausap.

179
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:30,400
Sa tuwing darating ako,

180
00:08:30,510 --> 00:08:32,110
sinasabi mong abala ka

181
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:33,980
o humanap ng dahilan para makawala.

182
00:08:34,510 --> 00:08:35,030
ano?

183
00:08:35,669 --> 00:08:37,669
Ayaw mo na akong kausapin?

184
00:08:38,390 --> 00:08:39,190
Hindi yun.

185
00:08:39,870 --> 00:08:40,960
Tapos ano yun?

186
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:43,320
ayos lang ako.

187
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:45,490
Maayos naman ako dito.

188
00:08:45,740 --> 00:08:47,940
Sa tingin mo hindi ko masasabi kung kamusta ka?

189
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:48,510
Ning Fei,

190
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:50,140
makinig kang mabuti.

191
00:08:50,600 --> 00:08:52,150
Pinutol ko na ang relasyon ko kay Xia Jingshi

192
00:08:52,150 --> 00:08:53,080
at Xiao Weiran.

193
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:54,940
Walang kinalaman sa iyo iyon.

194
00:08:54,940 --> 00:08:56,200
Wala kang ginawang mali.

195
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:58,030
Huwag pahirapan ang iyong sarili

196
00:08:58,030 --> 00:08:59,760
sa mga pagkakamali ng ibang tao.

197
00:09:00,230 --> 00:09:00,950
Pero...

198
00:09:02,240 --> 00:09:03,640
Bakit hindi mo ako hinayaang mamatay?

199
00:09:04,590 --> 00:09:06,790
Kung namatay ako, tapos na ang lahat.

200
00:09:06,910 --> 00:09:07,390
Kung ako ay namatay,

201
00:09:07,390 --> 00:09:09,190
Hindi ko na kailangang harapin ang lahat ng ito.

202
00:09:09,320 --> 00:09:10,790
Ang kapatid ko na minsang lumaban sa tabi ko

203
00:09:10,790 --> 00:09:11,920
naging kaaway ko na.

204
00:09:12,010 --> 00:09:13,080
Ang prinsipe na pinakapinagkatiwalaan ko

205
00:09:13,080 --> 00:09:14,410
niloko ako ng malupit.

206
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:16,000
Ako... hindi ko alam

207
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:17,480
kung ano ang kahulugan ng aking buhay.

208
00:09:17,480 --> 00:09:18,960
Isinaya ko ang lahat para iligtas ka,

209
00:09:18,960 --> 00:09:20,290
at gusto mo na lang mamatay?

210
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:21,720
Kung pinahahalagahan mo ang iyong buhay nang napakaliit,

211
00:09:21,720 --> 00:09:23,720
bakit kita niligtas nung una?

212
00:09:24,390 --> 00:09:25,120
Makinig ka sa akin.

213
00:09:25,870 --> 00:09:26,600
wala naman

214
00:09:26,600 --> 00:09:27,720
mas mahalaga kaysa manatiling buhay.

215
00:09:27,720 --> 00:09:28,720
Kahit na ito ay para sa aking kapakanan,

216
00:09:28,720 --> 00:09:29,870
dapat mabuhay ka ng maayos!

217
00:09:38,720 --> 00:09:40,120
Pero kung nalaman ko lang ng mas maaga

218
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:41,240
kung ano talaga sila,

219
00:09:41,240 --> 00:09:42,570
Binalaan sana kita.

220
00:09:43,000 --> 00:09:43,720
Hindi mo sana

221
00:09:43,720 --> 00:09:44,980
muntik nang mawalan ng buhay.

222
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:47,200
Isa lang akong tanga.

223
00:09:48,080 --> 00:09:48,910
Anong karapatan ko

224
00:09:48,910 --> 00:09:49,910
maging kapatid mo?

225
00:09:49,910 --> 00:09:51,320
Hindi ako karapatdapat na maging kapatid mo.

226
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:52,450
Iwan mo na lang ako.

227
00:09:52,790 --> 00:09:53,670
Iwan mo na lang ako.

228
00:09:53,670 --> 00:09:54,320
Ning Fei.

229
00:09:55,480 --> 00:09:56,790
Hindi naman ganoon kaseryoso.

230
00:09:57,790 --> 00:09:59,190
Kahit anong isipin mo,

231
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:01,200
palagi kang magiging kapatid ko.

232
00:10:05,030 --> 00:10:05,600
ano?

233
00:10:06,550 --> 00:10:07,440
Ayaw mo bang tumanda

234
00:10:07,440 --> 00:10:08,370
kasama ko na?

235
00:10:08,870 --> 00:10:09,720
ayaw mo ba

236
00:10:09,720 --> 00:10:10,910
para mamuhay ng walang pakialam sa piling ko

237
00:10:10,910 --> 00:10:12,570
sa magandang lugar na?

238
00:10:17,440 --> 00:10:18,030
Ning Fei,

239
00:10:19,670 --> 00:10:21,030
ikaw ang walang takot,

240
00:10:21,480 --> 00:10:22,440
matigas ang labanan,

241
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:24,100
numero unong heneral ng Jinxiu.

242
00:10:24,840 --> 00:10:25,910
lagi kong alam

243
00:10:26,440 --> 00:10:27,320
na wala

244
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:28,520
maaaring masira ka.

245
00:10:29,960 --> 00:10:31,020
Makinig ng mabuti.

246
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:33,030
Simula ngayon,

247
00:10:33,790 --> 00:10:35,650
dapat mong hilahin ang iyong sarili.

248
00:10:43,150 --> 00:10:44,280
Mas katulad yan.

249
00:10:45,320 --> 00:10:46,440
Kapatid ko yun.

250
00:10:47,360 --> 00:10:48,870
Yan ang Ning Fei na kilala ko.

251
00:10:52,750 --> 00:10:53,360
ate.

252
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:56,210
Feng Suige ay gising na.

253
00:11:08,790 --> 00:11:09,510
Feng Suige!

254
00:11:13,870 --> 00:11:15,510
Feng Suige, gising ka na.

255
00:11:16,270 --> 00:11:17,200
Salamat sa Diyos.

256
00:11:17,480 --> 00:11:18,740
Sa wakas gising ka na.

257
00:11:19,510 --> 00:11:20,030
Yixiao.

258
00:11:21,320 --> 00:11:22,030
